headline: 3 Growth Companies With High Insider Ownership Achieving Up To 26% Return On Equity
summary: As the U.S. market aims to extend its rally, with the S&P 500 and Nasdaq showing positive momentum, investors are keenly observing stocks that combine growth potential with solid insider ownership. In such a climate, companies demonstrating high returns on equity can be particularly appealing, as they often indicate strong management confidence and alignment with shareholder interests.

headline: Workday Chief Financial Officer to Present at the Jefferies Public Technology Conference on May 28, 2025
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people, money, and agents, today announced that Zane Rowe, chief financial officer, Workday, will present at the Jefferies Public Technology Conference on May 28, 2025 at 11:00 a.m. Pacific Time / 2:00 p.m. Eastern Time.
